&lt;p&gt;This is a foundational hire. You will build the deal desk function from the ground up, designing the workflows, templates, and approval frameworks for multiple business units. The right candidate is someone who can operate with precision in the details today — assembling order forms, maintaining Salesforce accuracy, routing approvals — while simultaneously building the systems and processes that will scale well beyond what&#39;s needed right now.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for someone who takes pride in operational excellence, thrives in building structure from ambiguity, and brings the commercial judgment and credibility needed to be a trusted partner to a fast-moving sales organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deal Structuring &amp;amp; Execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the end-to-end deal process from pricing through execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Sales to structure deals that align with pricing guidelines, discounting policies, and commercial standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assemble, review, and quality-check order forms and commercial documentation for accuracy and completeness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate cross-functional approvals across Finance, Legal, and GTM leadership, ensuring deals move through the pipeline without unnecessary friction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct final review of all deals prior to execution, serving as the last line of quality control before signature&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the pricing and commercial sections of RFP/RFI responses in partnership with Sales and PMM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Design &amp;amp; Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Build the deal desk function and the operational infrastructure to support it.&lt;/p&gt;
