&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain pricing guidelines, discount approval matrices, and deal structuring playbooks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and resolve recurring friction points in the deal cycle, driving process improvements that accelerate time-to-close while maintaining commercial discipline&lt;/li&gt;
