&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise on employment law matters, including employee relations, performance management, accommodations, investigations, wage and hour, and terminations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Counsel People and leadership teams on workforce strategy, organizational risk, and compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide practical guidance on federal, state, and local employment laws.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marketplace &amp;amp; Workforce Integrity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead legal strategy related to independent contractor classification and marketplace workforce models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise on marketplace products, onboarding flows, incentives, and contractor programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess regulatory and litigation risks tied to platform-based labor models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build scalable governance frameworks that support growth while mitigating workforce risk.&lt;/li&gt;
