&lt;li&gt;Experiment with new formats for how benchmarks, grants, and research collaborations reach and resonate with the research community.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spearhead and write technical content and campaigns for Snorkel on collaborations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
